channel.title: Can't get server online
channel.description:
Okay I am using Windows Xp and I have No-ip and an account. I have port-foward, I disabled my Virus Scanners and Firewalls. Added the 43594 port to my firewall list, had my server online I was logged in and my friend could not get on. WTF? Am I missing something? When I port-fowarded this is what I put in the boxes: [ul][li]In application I put Moparscape[/li] [li]In Start I put 43594[/li] [li]In end I put 43594 [/li] [li]In Protocol I put TCP [/li] [li]In IP address I put my Defualt Gateway Ip [/li][/ul]
And then I hit enable and saved it. Did I do something wrong?
